      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This car is the perfect blank canvas for someone who loves a challenge and getting their hands dirty. While it definitely needs a significant amount of mechanical and cosmetic TLC to get back to its prime, it offers a fantastic opportunity to own a vehicle at a fraction of the cost. If you're looking for a rewarding restoration project or a reliable source for parts, this is the one for you!",
