    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-maintained by its previous owner. The exterior retains a beautiful shine, though upon close inspection, you will find some minor surface scratches and a few small stone chips on the hood consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of major wear, though the driver's seat shows some light creasing. Mechanically, the car is sound, providing a smooth and confident driving experience. It is an excellent choice for a buyer looking for a dependable, high-quality vehicle that has many years of service left.",
